map_npcs.npc_dialog_post:
Why...
Me...
...
[That's all for the playtest session!]
[Feel free to continue adventuring!]
[And don't forget to let us know your throughts!]

Fine, fine, you can come in. 
Just don't expect everyone to be so... understandin'.
map_npcs.npc_dialog_pre:
Oh, you think you can just waltz right into our hideout?
Bad news for you buddy, its fightin' time.

map_npcs.npc_dialog_post:
And this is why I'm done with guard duty.
I'm really not any good at fighting.
map_npcs.npc_dialog_pre:
I hate working as a guard. That's why I'm hanging out here. 
Hey wait a minute, you're not supposed to be here!

map_npcs.npc_dialog_post:
Huh, I guess you took care of things instead.
I guess it can't hurt to let you have a little of the stash.
Check the chest behind me.
map_npcs.npc_dialog_pre:
Hehehe, we finally got our hands on some new tech.
Wait! You weren't supposed to hear that!
Guess I'll have to take care of things myself.

map_npcs.npc_dialog_post:
It almost seems like all the mushrooms in this cave are interconnected somehow...
Almost like the whole cave is one big organism.
map_npcs.npc_dialog_pre:
I heard some screaming from the tunnels . 
I hope whoever it was is okay.

map_npcs.npc_dialog_post: I have to get out of here!
Don't let that thing touch you!
map_npcs.npc_dialog_pre: No, no, no, not like this!

map_npcs.npc_dialog_post: Please, just leave me alone. I don't want to go back there.
map_npcs.npc_dialog_pre:
No, no, just go away!
Will this make you leave me alone?

map_npcs.npc_dialog_post:
Huh? What was that?
Oh, I must've dozed off a little.
map_npcs.npc_dialog_pre:
These caves really are beautiful...
I can barely... take my eyes off the...
Mushrooms...
Fight...?

map_shops.shop_greeting: Sure, sure you can shop here. But I'm charging you extra.
